ed="T" n="0835c16"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0835c16"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000034918"><placeName>成都</placeName><placeName>郫縣</placeName><placeName>法定寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A012471">惟忠</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0835c17"/><persName key="A012471">釋惟忠</persName>，少孺為僧，勵精自行，在乎群等，莫<lb
ed="T" n="0835c18"/>不宗焉。出家<placeName key="PL000000034918">法定寺</placeName>──本是後<placeName key="PL000000000098">漢</placeName><date notBefore-iso="+0058-02-11" key="j17422861748698" notAfter-iso="+0075-09-02"><name>永平</name>中</date>佛<lb
ed="T" n="0835c19"/>法始流<placeName key="PL000000000083">中國</placeName>便有，置<placeName key="PL000000034918">德淨伽藍</placeName>，神光屢現。<lb
ed="T" n="0835c20"/>至<placeName key="PL000000000136">宋</placeName><persName key="A002217">釋惠持</persName>自<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬阜</placeName>辭<persName key="A001204">遠<roleName>公</roleName></persName>法兄，誓化<placeName key="PL000000034777">岷<lb
ed="T" n="0835c21"/>蜀</placeName>。屬<persName key="A002836">譙縱</persName>不道，令數輩操刃欲屠<persName key="A002217">持</persName>。<persName key="A002217">持</persName>乃<lb
ed="T" n="0835c22"/>彈指，其眾驚奔僵仆。<placeName key="PL000000000105">隋</placeName><date from-iso="+0584-02-19" key="j19344111934764" to-iso="+0585-02-06"><name>開皇</name>四年</date>改名<placeName key="PL000000034918">法<lb
    ed="T" n="0835c23"/>定</placeName>焉。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000034918">寺</ref>有<persName key="A001428">彌勒</persName>聖像。<placeName key="PL000000000106">唐</placeName><date notBefore-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469511949949" notAfter-iso="+0626-09-05"><name>武德</name>中</date>忽有枯查<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1726"/><lb
ed="T" n="0835c24"/>沿江而至，夜發光明，因雕作像首。<date notBefore-iso="+0627-01-26" key="j19500921958296" notAfter-iso="+0649-07-13"><name>貞觀</name>中</date><lb
ed="T" n="0835c25"/><persName key="A005740">竇軌</persName>為長<anchor xml:id="beg0835sgsz19"/>吏<anchor xml:id="end0835sgsz19"/><placeName key="PL000000035743">劍門</placeName><ptr target="#n2589"/>，佛首光見引達于府。<persName key="A005740">竇<lb
ed="T" n="0835c26"/><roleName>公</roleName></persName>令人迎取，數百人亦不能勝。乃令祝之，<lb
ed="T" n="0835c27"/>任欲何往，遂言：「可就<placeName key="PL000000034918">法定</placeName>否？」乃一人能舉。<lb
ed="T" n="0835c28"/><persName key="A005740">竇</persName>遂造佛身，長史<ptr target="#n1888"/><persName key="A008886">高士廉</persName>蓋殿以安之。後<lb
ed="T" n="0835c29"/>有僧<persName key="A012472">汎愛</persName>樹其浮圖，而獲一巨蟹，身足二<pb ed="T" n="0836a" xml:id="T50.2061.0836a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0836a01"/>尺餘。是塔頗多靈異，人或將酒肉乘醉詣<lb
ed="T" n="0836a02"/>聖佛前，立見災禍矣。<persName key="A012471">忠</persName>於<date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15"><name>天寶</name>中</date>於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000034918">寺</ref>，愈<lb
ed="T" n="0836a03"/>加精苦。無何<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g493"/>，塔為霆震，拔其塔心柱出<lb
ed="T" n="0836a04"/>外，忽有小木承代之意，眾咸怪之，罔測厥<lb
ed="T" n="0836a05"/><anchor xml:id="beg0836sgsz1"/>由<anchor xml:id="end0836sgsz1"/>。<persName key="A012471">忠</persName>乃叩搕於聖<persName key="A001428">彌勒</persName>像，告訴天龍合加<lb
ed="T" n="0836a06"/>畏重，何輒震擊，奪塔心柱邪？是知庶女呌而<lb
ed="T" n="0836a07"/>雷擊<persName key="A023742">景公</persName>臺<ptr target="#n1889"/>，誠有所感。一日迅雷烈風，還<lb
ed="T" n="0836a08"/>同前震。覆覩之，乃龍神送舊柱，安置如故。<lb
ed="T" n="0836a09"/>當其易柱，陰雲四合，有四神人以身扶翼，<lb
ed="T" n="0836a10"/>立與塔<anchor xml:id="beg0836sgsz3"/>齊<anchor xml:id="end0836sgsz3"/>。<persName key="A012471">忠</persName>之感物也若此。<date from-iso="+0841-02-08" key="j20282682030170" to-iso="+0846-04-25"><name>會昌</name></date>坼<ref type="place" target="#PL000000034918">寺</ref>之<lb
ed="T" n="0836a11"/>前，舍利七粒出相輪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1727"/>上，白光滿空，向西飛<lb
ed="T" n="0836a12"/>去，<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>皆所<anchor xml:id="beg0836sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>自</sic><corr>目</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0836sgsz5"/>覩。將倒之時，赤光見于半天<lb
ed="T" n="0836a13"/>焉。又<ref type="place" target="#PL000000034918">此寺</ref>有大棗樹，將毀<ref type="place" target="#PL000000034918">寺</ref>之年，其樹枯<lb
ed="T" n="0836a14"/>瘁。及<date from-iso="+0847-02-10" key="j20304612035056" to-iso="+0859-09-10"><name>大中</name></date>再置，其棗重<anchor xml:id="beg0836sgsz7"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>樂</sic><corr>榮</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0836sgsz7"/>也。<persName key="A012471">忠</persName>後終<placeName key="PL000000034918"><anchor xml:id="beg0836001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>寺</sic><corr>于寺</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0836001"/></placeName>。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0836a1501"><lb
ed="T" n="0836a15"/>系曰：教法興替<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g522"/>，得非數乎？數算已定，晷刻弗<lb
ed="T" n="0836a16"/>移。如其<date from-iso="+0841-02-08" key="j20282682030170" to-iso="+0846-04-25"><name>會昌</name></date>之前，舍利預飛，棗樹先瘁，是<lb
ed="T" n="0836a17"/>知當替數之彊，興數必弱，興不勝其替矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0836a18"/><date from-iso="+0847-02-10" key="j20304612035056" to-iso="+0859-09-10"><name>大中</name></date>之興，替不勝其興矣。若不為四相<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1168"/>之<lb
ed="T" n="0836a19"/>遷，非<anchor xml:id="beg0836sgsz8"/>繫<anchor xml:id="end0836sgsz8"/>興替之數也。教法是有為之法<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1533"/>，詎<lb
ed="T" n="0836a20"/>免遷流者乎，吁！</p>
